      EPS_DEFAULT 1.0E-12
      METHOD xTB
      &XTB
        GFN_TYPE TBLITE
        &TBLITE
          METHOD GFN1
          ACCURACY 0.1
        &END TBLITE
      &END XTB
    &END QS
    &POISSON
      PERIODIC NONE
    &END POISSON
